##Vulcan Mountain Hospital began to receive patients today, the director of SARS prevention and treatment experts

Health insight

Functional introduction, understand the health professional news

* The 1,000-bed Vulcan Mountain Hospital began accepting patients today, mainly treating confirmed patients.
* 400 medical personnel from the military have arrived, and the director, Col. Zhang Sibing, is an expert in SARS prevention and control.
* The 1,600 bed Raytheon Hospital is due to be completed on February 5.
* To a certain extent, the use of hospitals can alleviate the difficulties of new pneumonia patients in Wuhan, and also help to reduce panic.

The 1,000-bed Vulcan Mountain Hospital began accepting patients today, mainly treating confirmed patients.

1,400 military medical personnel have arrived, and the hospital's director, Col. Zhang Sibing, is an expert in SARS prevention and control.

The 1,600-bed Raytheon Hospital is due to be completed on February 5.

To some extent, the operation of the two hospitals can alleviate the difficult situation of new pneumonia patients in Wuhan, and also help to reduce panic.

Wuhan Huoshenshan new crown pneumonia specialist hospital, which was ordered to accept patients today, the main treatment of confirmed patients.

The 1,000-bed hospital, which began construction on January 24, was officially delivered yesterday (February 2) , taking 10 days and involving about 7,500 builders. The site's 24-hour live feed was viewed by more than 80 million people.

Yesterday morning, 950 medical and nursing personnel from the hospital under the Joint Logistics Support Unit arrived in Wuhan from Shenyang, Lanzhou, Nanjing and Guangzhou, together with 450 medical staff from the Army Medical University, the Naval Medical University and the Air Force Medical University, who have supported Wuhan for nearly 10 days and were the first to arrive, a medical team of 1,400 people has been formed, to undertake the medical treatment task of Vulcan Mountain Hospital.

Dean Zhang Sibing, a former head of the 301 Military Hospital's 301 Military Hospital, was also on the scene yesterday. He was born in 1969 and took part in the 2003 campaign against SARS and the construction of Xiaotangshan Hospital, according to public records.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Delta plot

Zhang sibing has published several papers on the prevention and treatment of SARS, such as the study on SARS diagnosis, discharge criteria and hospital admission strategies, and the medical protection of Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome, among which he is the third author, the fourth author is Zhang Yanling, director of Beijing Xiaotangshan Hospital.

Mount Vulcan and the Thor Mountain Hospital, due to be completed on February 5, are known as the "Xiaotangshan" in Wuhan. Xiaotangshan Hospital received 680 SARS patients, of which 672 recovered and were discharged, and none of the 1,383 medical staff involved in treatment and care were infected, which is considered a turning point of SARS prevention and treatment in Beijing.

Xiaotangshan Hospital was established at a time when the SARS epidemic was at its most intense in Beijing. The hospital was in an emergency with a gap of 1,500 to 2,000 beds. "I felt terrible, " Zhang said later. "there were so many patients that there was no room for them. Even the doctors who treated them were falling down. "

At this time, Wuhan, also urgent, 8:00 Jianwen two days ago Article "undiagnosed new crown cases: hidden behind the statistics of life story, " the patient faced with the difficulties of diagnosis, admission difficulties. As of yesterday afternoon, only one of the patients interviewed at the time had been admitted to hospital, while the others were still waiting.

There are currently 6,754 beds in the three designated hospitals opened in Wuhan. On February 2, it was proposed that the two designated hospitals to be renovated and opened would be able to add 2,183 beds, plus 1,000 beds in the Mount Vulcan and 1,600 beds in the Mount Thor, the dilemma can be alleviated to some extent.

Xiong lize, a former director of the intensive-care unit and now director of the Shanghai No. 4 People's Hospital, told Xinmin Weekly that the more important role of the temporary hospital after its opening is to increase the cure rate and reduce the mortality rate, reduce social anxiety.

Source: CCTV screenshot

##

How to build a hospital in ten days

Different from Xiaotangshan, the names of the two emergency hospitals are not directly derived from the place names, but are endowed with special meanings.

Hubei is the land of Ancient Chu, and in the legends of the Chu Culture, the people of the state of Chu are believed to be descendants of the god of fire, Zhu Rong. The five elements of the human lung metal, Huokejin, and poison the human lung COVID-19 fear high temperature, fire God just can drive away the god of plague, so the name "Fire God mountain" was born.

For the past 10 days, builders have been working in double shifts on a site the size of seven football fields. Alongside the anti-epidemic jitters are the cute names and cheers given to forklifts (fork sauce) , excavators (minions) and cement pumps (vomit sauce) on construction sites by viewers watching the live video.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
##The construction of Mount Vulcan:

The construction of Mount Vulcan:

On the afternoon of January 23, the Wuhan Urban Renewal Authority held an emergency meeting to request the construction of a special hospital following the model of Beijing Xiaotangshan Hospital during the 2003 SARS outbreak

January 24, New Year's Eve, the first day, the completion of the relevant design, hundreds of excavators arrived at the site, the beginning of land formation;

January 25, the first day of the Lunar New Year, the second day, the official start;

January 26, the second day of the Lunar New Year, the third day, the first model building completed;

January 27, the third day of the Lunar New Year, the 4th day, the site leveling, Gravel Sand backfilling all completed;

January 28, the fourth day of the Lunar New Year, the 5th day, the double-deck Ward Steel Structure Initially took shape;

January 29, the fifth day of the Lunar New Year, the 6th day, more than 300 box-type board room frame installation completed;

January 30, the sixth day of the Lunar New Year, the seventh day, the anti-seepage Membrane laying was completed;

January 31, the seventh day of the Lunar New Year, the 8th day, 9 into the Container Assembly has been completed, movable board housing frame installation 3000 square meters;

February 1, the eighth day of the Lunar New Year, the 9th day, fully launched the installation of medical equipment;

February 2, the ninth day of the Lunar New Year, day 10, delivery.

##Hospital facilities

Hospital facilities

Ten days to build out of the hospital, what is the internal environment? Follow the CCTV live broadcast yesterday afternoon, you can go to see.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
There are two beds in each ward. There are cabinets and medical equipment beside the beds.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The oxygen pipeline is an important infrastructure.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Air-conditioning and ventilation ducts to ensure that the air delivered to the room has been purified, and each room is equipped with an air purifier.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The special isolation transmission cabin of the Infectious Disease Ward is used for the transmission of medical materials, medicine and food. The ultraviolet system is used to sterilize the transmission cabin to avoid infection.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Each ward with a separate toilet, toilet with a water heater, toilet, sink and other basic supplies.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
A television was also installed in the ward.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Disinfection lamps are installed in the corridor of the ward.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Where medical waste water goes is an important issue, and for Infectious Disease Hospitals, it is the key to epidemic prevention. Previously, Tang Qun, deputy chief architect of CITIC ARCHITECTURAL DESIGN & Research Institute Co. , Ltd. and Chief Executive of huoshenshan design, said in an 8:00 Jianwen interview, huoshenshan hospital has adopted the Technical Measures of rainwater collection and disinfection and anti-seepage Membrane laying all over the base. The 50,000 square meters of construction land is covered with anti-seepage membrane, the sewage is disinfected for 4 hours and then discharged into the city pipe network, and the site rainwater is collected through a special system, disinfected for half an hour and then discharged into the city pipe network, medical waste shall be disposed of in accordance with the relevant regulations of the Environmental Protection Department.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Design and Research Institute of CITIC

As an isolation treatment hospital for infectious diseases, Huoshenshan hospital has high requirements for protection and isolation. According to Tang, cross-infection can be avoided by setting up clean areas, semi-polluted areas, polluted areas, special passageways for medical staff and patients, and corresponding ventilation systems from zero-pressure clean spaces to negative-pressure wards. Medical staff in and out of the ward set up special health facilities, including drenching, to maximize the protection of health and safety of medical staff.

The Dean is an expert in the prevention and treatment of SARS

According to the official website of the Fourth Military Medical University, Zhang Sibing, the director of Huoshenshan Hospital, is an expert in the management of medical care and health care and graduated from the 88th Oral Department of the former Fourth Military Medical University, former 309 hospital dental physicians, 301 Military Hospital director, 301 Military Hospital, director of the medical department, 301 Military Hospital, and other posts.

Zhang sibing participated in the fight against SARS, published many papers on SARS, mainly to explore the SARS designated hospitals to improve the cure rate, reduce mortality, strive for "zero" infection strategy.

In addition to Xiaotangshan's achievements, he and other authors, Zhang Yanling, in the Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome, also noted: (2003) the PLA 309 hospital treated 202 SARS patients in three months, fever clinic admitted more than 2500 cases of fever patients, there are 248 medical staff in turn to work in the prevention of "SARS" front line, are not infected with SARS.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
1,400 medics in position

According to the Air Force News, in the early morning of February 2, the air force dispatched eight large transport planes, which took off from a military airport one after another, and arrived in Shenyang, Lanzhou, Guangzhou, Nanjing and other places one after another at 4 a.m, it started carrying 795 members of the military medical team and 58 tons of supplies before taking off again for Wuhan. Starting at 8:55 a.m. , eight large transport planes landed at Wuhan Tianhe Airport at five-minute intervals. At noon, the army organized all the medical forces in place.
Source: CCTV screenshot

Huoshenshan hospital set up intensive care unit, Intensive Care Unit, General Unit, set up infection control, testing, special diagnosis, radiation diagnosis and other auxiliary departments.

In an interview with CCTV, Shen Lie, director of the Health Service Department of Wuxi Joint Logistics Support Center, said that unlike in the past, this time in addition to medical and nursing personnel, a team of management, information and service support personnel was selected, to meet the operational requirements of the new hospital.

Prior to the departure, the medical team had already undergone three days of completely closed management training and had established 28 programmes in four areas, namely administration, medical care, personal protection and logistic support, and invited experts in respiratory, infectious, and critical care medicine to teach.

In addition to the 1,400 medical personnel from various medical institutions in the military region, 15 experts from the People's Liberation Army Center for Disease Control and Prevention and the Military Medical Research Institute of the Chinese Academy of Military Sciences have also been drawn to form a joint expert group to guide the work of epidemic prevention and control in the hospital. Many of the medical staff have participated in the Xiaotangshan Hospital to combat SARS mission and to assist Sierra Leone, Liberia to combat the Ebola epidemic mission, has rich experience in the treatment of infectious diseases.
Can the miracle of Xiao Tangshan Be Repeated

Xiaotangshan was built during the SARS crisis in Beijing and later became the turning point of SARS prevention and control.

"Some experts assert that if there were no Xiaotangshan Hospital, Beijing would have at least 2,000 to 3,000 more SARS patients and at least 200 more deaths, " Zhang said in "looking back at Xiaotangshan. ".
△ PICTURE SOURCE: "looking back at Xiaotangshan" screenshot

After 17 years, Vulcan Mountain learned a lot from Xiaotangshan. Zhang Yanling was invited to serve as expert consultant of specialized hospitals. In his opinion, the scale and quality of construction, scientific rationality of design and equipment of Huoshenshan Hospital and Leishenshan hospital are better and higher than Xiaotangshan Hospital.

Tian Yi, an architect at CITIC ARCHITECTURAL DESIGN & Research Institute, told Jianwen at eight o'clock that the Xiaotangshan Hospital's large ward is separate and independent. To travel from one area to another, one can only go through the open air, and the patient's passageways are directly open to the outside world and are not closed. According to the opinion of Xiaotangshan Hospital and Wuhan Medical Expert Group, Huoshenshan Hospital keeps the medical and patient flow lines in the room, and isolates them separately. The medical staff can reach each ward through the building's medical cleaning corridor, which does not need to reach the outside, thus effectively protecting the safety of the medical staff. And the Vulcan Ward uses a container room that didn't exist 17 years ago.

Now, the number of confirmed cases of new pneumonia has exceeded the number of SARS, Vulcan Mountain Hospital is expected.

Why Must Wuhan be built in core epidemic area fire God mountain, Thunder God Mountain Hospital? Zhang made four points, according to the Changjiang Daily:
First, it is imperative to alleviate the current problem of too many patients, overloading existing hospitals and not being admitted to them.
The second is to enable these patients to receive formal, standardized treatment.
Third, centralized treatment, reducing the spread of infectious diseases, spread of the region.
Fourth, build up confidence in the people.
